# CODEOWNERS — required reviewers per path.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner> [more owners...]
# Multiple owners on a single line means ANY of them can approve.
# Last matching pattern wins, so put the catch-all first and refine below.
#
# Reviewers are added to PRs automatically based on the files touched.
# Once branch protection is set to require CODEOWNERS review, a PR
# can't merge until one matching owner approves it.

# Catch-all — every PR needs at least one of these reviewers.
